_sText:
It's been done before, maybe, but never like this. The itemboxes *actually work* and give random weapons each round. There is also a functional "radar" above the middle of the map, only precise enough to show if someone is in a color and what team they are on. There are several secrets throughout the map, just keep an eye out. 

UnRAR and drop the .bsp in your cstrike/maps folder. All sounds and textures are pak'd into the .bsp for your convenience. Enjoy!

URLs to credit the condributions can be seen at team selection.
